name: Tumble_Weed
content:
Tumble Weed was the name of a makrin creeper that lived on Makeb until 3639 BBY, when it was killed.
Tumble Weed appears in the Star Wars: The Old Republic: Rise of the Hutt Cartel expansion to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as a Champion boss on Makeb. He is not directly involved in any quests, but can be killed for loot and as part of the achievement. This article assumes 100% game completion, which means he was killed.
